articles.title: SA fightback after Ravindra's strikes in Hamilton - Rediff.com
articles.description: All-rounder Rachin Ravindra continued to bolster his reputation with three for 33 as New Zealand reduced a weakened but battling South Africa side to 220 for six on the first day of the second Test at Seddon Park on Tuesday.
